{"word":"G389 - ἀναστενάζω - anastenázō - an-as-ten-ad'-zo - Sigh deeply","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀναστενάζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">anastenázō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-as-ten-ad'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Sigh deeply</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பெருமூச்சுவிடு"},{"paragraph":"to draw sighs up frown the bottom of the breast, to sigh deeply"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G303 - ἀνά - aná - an-ah'/303\">G303</a> and <a href=\"#/G4727 - στενάζω - stenázō - sten-ad'-zo/4727\">G4727</a>; to <i>sigh deeply:</i> - sigh deeply.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}